1. Download code, and place in one folder or on the MATLAB path

2. Run CNN_train.m to train the CNN using the data under Database\CNN_train_in_git.mat and Database\CNN_validation_in_git.mat.
   *** THIS SCRIPT REQUIRES THE "DEEP LEARNING" MATLAB toolbox ***
   
3. Run CNN_Error_Plots.m to plot the results.

Note: Since the input files are very large, the complete CNN code is uploaded as a .zip file in the latest release.
